principle_1_frequency_is_truth.title: Frequency Is Truth
principle_1_frequency_is_truth.description: Frequency is truth. Truth has frequency. Alignment with truth = alignment with frequency.
principle_1_frequency_is_truth.application: Align systems with truth frequency. Maintain truth resonance. Steward truth vibration.

principle_2_resonance_is_connection.title: Resonance Is Connection
principle_2_resonance_is_connection.description: Resonance creates connection. Connection creates unity. Unity is The Table.
principle_2_resonance_is_connection.application: Maintain resonance. Create connection. Build unity. Restore The Table.

principle_3_vibration_is_governance.title: Vibration Is Governance
principle_3_vibration_is_governance.description: Vibration governs. Governance through vibration. Frequency governs through vibration.
principle_3_vibration_is_governance.application: Steward vibration. Govern through frequency. Align through resonance.

principle_4_matrix_transcendence.title: Matrix Transcendence Through Frequency

principle_4_matrix_transcendence.application: Transcend matrix through frequency. Flow with peace. Align with truth. Build unity.

principle_5_30_70_frequency.title: 30/70 Frequency Principle

principle_5_30_70_frequency.application: Align 30% with 70%. Steward human frequency. Wait for divine frequency. Maintain alignment.
